- Uses `prepareImages()` helper to normalize image input
- Calls `this.processor()` on image to get `pixel_values`
- Uses `this.tokenizer()` to create special task prompts with decoder input IDs
- Passes both `pixel_values` and `decoder_input_ids` to `this.model.generate()`
- Parses regex to extract answer from generated text
- Uses `this.model.config.decoder.max_position_embeddings` to set generation max_length
